Coating soft white fish fillets in batter and frying until the crust turns crisp while hot chips cook in the next tray for a simple fish and chips style meal!🐟🍟 Stacking the fried fish fillet in a bun or on a plate with chips, squeezing lemon over the top, and serving a calm village take on filet o fish at home!🏡✨

00:00 – 03:55 Catching & Filleting the Fish
03:55 – 08:33 Crispy Batter (Battered Fish Fillets)
08:33 – 11:25 Chip-Shop Style Fries
11:05 – 12:25 Soft Buns (Quick Bake)
12:25 – 18:13 Frying the Fish + Fish Sandwich Build
